description: Thank you for coming to our first U1 event of the year! Big round of applause for our winners and runner ups, as well as our wonderful U1 rep, Moyọ 🌟 You’re all rockstars! We hope you had fun, and we’ll see you at our next event 🤩 p.s. it involves wine…

Get ready for DESA’s most beloved event! 🍷 On November 27th, join DESA, your favourite English professors, and fellow English students in Arts 160 for a night of wine, crackers and cheese, and a little bit of networking 😉 come hang out with us! ps: swipe for last year’s photos!
DESA is inviting all U1 students to participate in our spinoff of "Who Wants To Be A Millionaire?" on Thursday, November 14th! 🏆 Join us for a fun night of trivia, chatting, and prizes!

English Department merch is NOW AVAILABLE! Find the order form in the link in our bio. Get it now before it’s all gone!🪶🐦‍⬛

This year features the return of burgundy, forest green, navy, and black designs, along with embroidery options. A QR Code is also up at our book sale in the Leacock Lobby!
